name: InteNet
description: InteNet Protocol is an integrated DeFAI (Decentralized Finance for AI) layer designed to empower AI agents with decentralized financial capabilities. InteNet Protocol is an innovative DeFAI platform designed to cater to token launch, liquidity management, and automated market operations for AI agents. With features such as a Launchpad, a Native DEX, and AI Agent Modules, InteNet Protocol offers a seamless experience for AI Agent token issuance, trading, liquidity management, DeFi strategy execution, and embedded AI features.
